      "message": "validation: Don't add pruned blocks to m_blocks_unlinked on startup\n\nLoadBlockIndex() adds to m_blocks_unlinked based only on nTx > 0, without\nchecking BLOCK_HAVE_DATA. Pruning preserves nTx but clears BLOCK_HAVE_DATA,\nso a pruned block whose parent was header-only gets re-added on every\nrestart, causing the CheckBlockIndex() assertion that entries must have\ndata on disk to fail.\n\nCheck that BLOCK_HAVE_DATA is set before inserting into m_blocks_unlinked.\n\nFixes #35050.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "marcofleon",
        "email": "marleo23@proton.me",
        "date": "2026-04-27T17:16:44Z"
      },
      "author": {
        "name": "marcofleon",
        "email": "marleo23@proton.me",
        "date": "2026-04-27T17:16:44Z"
      },
      "sha": "0e4b0bacecf94063342c7f9eb9b03dac8a7a7936"
    },
